The RCR Specular Signature framework provides a unified mathematical resolution for global instabilities (climate, economic, social) by proving them to be manifestations of a single underlying failure: the violation of the Bounded Reciprocity condition. Its purpose is to model and implement self-stabilizing systems that achieve coherence through the continuous, recursive management of systemic friction.

